name: Tulle Cream Peacoat, XS
description: A lovely cream front-button coat made by Tulle.  Very warm.  Easy to dress up or down.  Features two front pockets and a fun yellow and cream inner lining.  Hits mid- to upper-thigh.  Runs large--this coat is an X-Small and fits more like a Small.  I am 5'2" and it is a bit too long and big in the shoulders.  Originally purchased from Nordstrom.

name: Tulle Plaid Pocket Dress, XS
description: An absolutely darling orange and cream plaid dress, featuring an elastic cinched waist, small pocket on the top, and two pockets in the skirt.  Super soft fabric.  Skirt hits just above the knee.  Looks great belted or with a cardigan (see the cream Tulle cardi!).  Runs slightly large on top.  100% cotton.  By Tulle.  BRAND NEW WITH TAGS!  Email for more pictures.

name: Anthropologie Sky Wings Sweater, XS
description: A lightweight, short-sleeved sweater shell in the sweetest light blue color.  Faux wrap waist design with ruffle detailing on each shoulder.  Polyester/cotton/rayon blend.  By Ric Rac, purchased from Anthropologie.
